Fourth Department,

January, 1945.

(January 10, 1945.) Maryland Casualty Company, Respondent, v. 16 North Goodman Street, Inc., Appellant.

Motion for reargument denied; motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Dowling, Harris, McCurn and Larkin, JJ. [See ante, p. 953.]
